	tagname
		Working with multiple elements


All method calls will do a freshness check to ensure that the element reference is still valid.This essentially determines whether or not the element is still attached to the DOM. If this testfails, then an StaleElementReferenceException is thrown, and allfuture calls to this instance will fail.

Exceptions from Selenium 
StaleElementReferenceException- Click method
NoSuchElementException- When selenium is not able to find on web page

