Timeout
		implicitlyWait
			Global wait
				It applies to all element
				Polling until element or timeout expire
				polling frequency is 250ms
				It has be after get method
				Do not add this wait multiple times


		pageLoadTimeout
			It will keep on waiting for page load till specified time if it does not load
			it will throw exception
			Applied to complete session
			It has be added before get method
			Do not add this wait multiple times


		setScriptTimeout

			Sets the amount of time to wait for an asynchronous script to finish execution beforethrowing an error. If the timeout is negative, then the script will be allowed to runindefinitely.


