Exception
	Any abnormal condition
		Checked Exception
			compiletime exception

		UnChecked exception 
			Runtime exception

Exception is a class, every exception parent class is Exception and Exception parent class is Throwable

Throwable parent class is Object

try catch- Only way
throw
throws

Exception Handling- process where you can handle the exception and terminate code gracefully

